 9.9.1-6 scaffold includes Woodstox for a StaxBridge-specific test, but that is not required for baseline meaningful Saxon coverage and is already part of the existing test project rather than new driver setup.\",\n    \"The reported failure is API drift in existing tests between 9.9.1-6 and 10.0, not evidence of missing dependency, Docker, or environment setup.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ddde033426b25f3016a2984ac84508194961fe5924890ce3d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2584, "output": 972, "cacheRead": 27648, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 31204, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781105816679, "responseId": "resp_0ddde033426b25f3016a29849934c48194bbba767d76830864"}, "toolResults": []}
